%% FCFS (First-Come, First-Served) Request Flow
%% Mermaid sequence diagram

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as 클라이언트
    participant API as API 계층
    participant FCFS as FCFS Scheduler
    participant Queue as BullMQ Queue
    participant Worker as Worker
    participant LLM as LLM Service

    Client->>API: POST /api/requests
    API->>FCFS: submit(request)
    FCFS->>Queue: add(request, {priority: 0})
    Queue-->>FCFS: jobId
    FCFS-->>API: requestId
    API-->>Client: 202 Accepted

    Note over Queue,Worker: 선착순 처리 (FIFO)
    
    Worker->>Queue: getNextJob()
    Queue-->>Worker: job (가장 오래된 요청)
    Worker->>LLM: processRequest(prompt)
    LLM-->>Worker: response
    Worker->>Queue: markCompleted(jobId)
    
    Client->>API: GET /api/requests/:id
    API-->>Client: {status: "completed", result: "..."}
